# Architecture (Angular Standalone + Feature-based)

- `app/core/` — API client, config, utilities (each unit in its own folder).
- `app/shared/` — reusable UI components and pipes (nested folders).
- `app/features/` — product features; each component/service/model in its own folder.
- `app/` — bootstrap only.

```typescript
// ✅ correct
import { ApiClientService } from '@core/api/api-client/api-client.service';
